name: Gold Stork - 2 EGLD for Ukraine (Tier 4)
description: A collection of 10 Storks, the national bird of Ukraine, born during the EGLD-for-Ukraine campaign in March of 2022. The Elrond community donated EGLD to support the peace effort in Ukraine. The bigger the donation, the more prestigious the Stork.
creator: Arda + ENFT DAO
